					<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content"><div class="mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang="en" dir="ltr"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Iranian paramilitary volunteer militia</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">
</p>
<table class="infobox vcard"><caption class="infobox-title fn org">Basij</caption><tbody><tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-subheader">بسیج</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-image logo"><span class="mw-default-size" typeof="mw:File/Frameless"><a href="/wiki/File:Basij_logo.png" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/3/33/Basij_logo.png/220px-Basij_logo.png" decoding="async" width="220" height="178" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/3/33/Basij_logo.png 1.5x" data-file-width="234" data-file-height="189" /></a></span></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-image logo"><span class="mw-default-size" typeof="mw:File/Frameless"><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_Basij.svg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7a/Flag_of_Basij.svg/220px-Flag_of_Basij.svg.png" decoding="async" width="220" height="160" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7a/Flag_of_Basij.svg/330px-Flag_of_Basij.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7a/Flag_of_Basij.svg/440px-Flag_of_Basij.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="1408" data-file-height="1026" /></a></span><div class="infobox-caption">بسیج</div></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label" style="padding-right:0.6em;">Formation</th><td class="infobox-data note">26&#160;November 1979<span class="noprint">&#59;&#32;44 years ago</span><span style="display:none">&#160;(<span class="bday dtstart published updated">1979-11-26</span>)</span> (decreed)<sup id="cite_ref-IPP_1-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-IPP-1">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br />30&#160;April 1980<span class="noprint">&#59;&#32;43 years ago</span><span style="display:none">&#160;(<span class="bday dtstart published updated">1980-04-30</span>)</span> (founded)<sup id="cite_ref-IPP_1-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-IPP-1">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="inf